Manage skills (Sprint 7 §7)

Usage: skill <COMMAND>

Commands:
  preview  Validate a manifest without installing. Returns the provenance digest + the parsed cap
           set so an operator can audit before committing
  install  Install a skill under the user discovery root
  list     List installed skills
  remove   Remove an installed skill by name
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help
